de.unibox.config

Class InternalConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.unibox.config.InternalConfig

  • public class InternalConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    Use this Class to configure more then just the logging level. You can activate logging by depending on your functional level. Furthermore you are able to set the database credentials and host directly here.
